tastingDescription:
&ldquo;Like opening a box of chocolates and hungrily inhaling the aromas of fruity chocolate, caramel, and soft centers. In addition, there are crystalized orange slices, fresh plum, black cherry, moist coffee grounds, and petrichor. Flavours of chocolate-dipped raspberries, gingersnaps, and bold sherry fruit from the oloroso finish. It&rsquo;s a dance between the smoke and the fruit, with the smoke ultimately pushed to the fringes, leaving a spiced mocha finish.&rdquo;
92 Points, Whisky Advocate 2019
3 Bottle Limit
